odal js-modal-close">                <div class="modal-dialog">                     <div class="modal-content js-modal-content">                          <button class="button-close js-modal-button" title="Close (Esc)" aria-label="Close (Esc)">×</button>                                              <picture>                  <img class="modal-image js-modal-image" src="/assets/TS-19618-1200x675-PayPalImage_MainImage_1446373808206_tcm1488-262770.jpg" width="1200" height="675" alt="Fund your 888poker account with PayPal" loading="lazy">     </picture>                      </div>                </div>           </div>       </div> </div>                 <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component None None">     <div class="text"><p>PayPal is one of the world's leading online payment processors. If you've never used PayPal, you may wonder why so many people rely on it to pay for almost everything they buy online. Here are the 5 main advantages of using this online payment method:</p><h2>1. It Protects Your Personal Details</h2><p>When you open a PayPal account, you link it to the credit cards and bank accounts you want to use for making payments online. You only do this one time. Your financial details are then saved to the PayPal secure system, where they get highly encrypted, so the only person who can see them is you.</p><p>Once your PayPal account is set up, you never have to share your credit card details or bank account info with anyone again. You can pay for stuff online with the confidence that hackers can't just download your personal info from the merchants you purchase from.</p><h2>2. It's Free to Use</h2><p>One of the most attractive benefits of using PayPal is that it's free. There is no yearly administration fee, no processing fees or service fees.</p><h2>3. It Saves You Time</h2><p>With PayPal, your funds are transferred within minutes from you clicking the mouse or tapping the screen. It saves you way more time compared to using other payment methods like bank transfer, wire transfer or prepaid vouchers, which you have to go out and purchase from a physical location.</p><h2>4. It's Flexible and Reliable</h2><p>Never experience the embarrassment of a declined payment attempt again. With PayPal, you can link several bank accounts, credit cards and debit cards to your account. Because it has more than one source of funds to draw from, you can be confident that payments will always be successful on the first try.</p><h2>How to use PayPal at 888poker</h2><p>It's so easy, just follow these steps:</p><ol><li>Login to 888poker and click <strong>Cashier</strong>.</li><li>Click <strong>Deposit</strong>.</li><li>You'll see icons for all of 888poker's accepted deposit methods. Click on the <strong>PayPal</strong> icon.</li><li>The PayPal deposit page will open. Enter the sum you want to deposit and click <strong>Submit</strong>.</li><li>Click <strong>Continue</strong> on the next page.</li><li>You'll be redirected to a PayPal login page. Enter your email and PayPal password to access your account.</li><li>Review your payment details and click <strong>Pay</strong>.</li><li>You'll be redirected to the 888poker Cashier, where you'll be get a transaction confirmation.</li></ol><p>To view the list of countries where PayPal is available, <a href="/real-money-poker/deposit/payment-methods/" target="_blank">click here</a></p></div> </div></div>   </div>                  </div>                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="sidebar">            <div class="sidebar-component">          <a href="/real-money-poker/" class="sidebar-title">Real Money Poker</a>             <div id="sidebar-menu" class="sidebar-menu js-custom-simplebar custom-simplebar dark-simplebar">                          <div class="sidebar-menu-item">                   <a href="/real-money-poker/cashout/" class="for-item">Cashout</a>               </div>                          <div c